headline: Monster Energy execs purchase Thrifty ice cream business
summary: A holding company, linked to Hilton Schlosberg and Rodney Sacks, paid $19.2 million for the Rite Aid-owned brand and a healthcare business.

headline: Monster Beverage Corp (MNST) rated a ‘Buy’ at Stifel on Sales Growth Prospects
summary: Monster Beverage Corporation (NASDAQ:MNST) is one of the 12 best consumer goods stocks billionaires are quietly buying.
